OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774620679
OL,3,CSquirrels willing to climb higher to
OL,4,Creach favourite food, study finds
OL,6,FSquirrels are willing to climb higher
OL,7,Fto reach their favourite foods,
OL,8,Fresearchers at the University of
OL,9,FExeter have found.
OL,11,FIn the study, wild grey squirrels were
OL,12,Foffered almond pieces or pumpkins
OL,13,Fseeds.
OL,15,FThe almond pieces ` their preferred
OL,16,Fsnack ` and pumpkin seeds were placed
OL,17,Fon poles of varying heights.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
