PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774620679
OL,3,CSquirrels willing to climb higher to
OL,4,Creach favourite food, study finds
OL,6,FResearchers found the squirrels'
OL,7,Fpreference for almonds only reduced
OL,8,Fslightly when the pieces were raised
OL,9,Fhigher off the ground, meaning a
OL,10,Flonger climb.
OL,12,FYavanna Burnham, from the University
OL,13,Fof Exeter, said: "The squirrels in our
OL,14,Fstudy were willing to work harder for
OL,15,Fthe better food.
OL,17,F"This suggests that ` in natural
OL,18,Fdecision-making scenarios ` it may
OL,19,Fsometimes be beneficial for animals to
OL,20,Fwait or work harder for a better
OL,21,Foutcome.
OL,26,@uD@ROUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
