PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774620679
OL,3,CSquirrels willing to climb higher to
OL,4,Creach favourite food, study finds
OL,6,F"This is what we would expect to find
OL,7,Fand it shows the value of doing
OL,8,Fresearch on wild animal populations."
OL,10,FThe study also found that less
OL,11,Fdominant squirrels were more likely to
OL,12,Fchoose easy-to-access food.
OL,14,FThis is potentially because they face
OL,15,Fa higher risk of losing the hard-to-
OL,16,Freach option if a rival appears.
OL,18,FDr Lisa Leaver, from the University of
OL,19,FExeter, added: "This study helps us
OL,20,Funderstand how animals decide how much
OL,21,Ftime and effort to invest.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@eO]{D@POU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
