OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774620679
OL,3,CSquirrels willing to climb higher to
OL,4,Creach favourite food, study finds
OL,6,F"It shows there isn't always an
OL,7,F'optimal' decision, and - just as with
OL,8,Fhumans - an animal's social status
OL,9,Faffects the costs and benefits of
OL,10,Fparticular choices.
OL,12,F"It's rational for different squirrels
OL,13,Fto assess the situation and adjust the
OL,14,Famount of time and energy they will
OL,15,Fexpend accordingly, in order to get a
OL,16,Freward."
OL,18,FThe study, which was funded by the
OL,19,FNatural Environment Research Council,
OL,20,Fwas carried out at the University of
OL,21,FExeter's Streatham Campus.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@HO]
