OL,3,CSquirrels willing to climb higher to
OL,4,Creach favourite food, study finds
OL,6,FIn total, 11 squirrels took part in
OL,7,Fthe tests and made more than 4,000
OL,8,Ffood preference choices, researchers
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FPole Position: Social Influences On
OL,12,FDiscounting Behaviour In Wild Grey
OL,13,FSquirrels is published in the journal
OL,14,FAnimal Behaviour.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
